"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-sport-paris-olympics-2024-gayton-mckenzie-wishes-tatjana-smith-well-in-retirement-latest-news\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.8715241161844238, \"rank\": 0.14715776416237053, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bbSport\\u00bbParis Olympics 2024\\u00bbGayton McKenzie wishes Tatjana Smith well in retirement  Minister of Sport, Arts and Culture, Gayton McKenzie has reacted to the announcement of Tatjana Smith's retirement.\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 376, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.8715241161844238, \"rank\": 0.14715776416237053, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}, {\"begin\": 204, \"end\": 219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton_McKenzie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gayton McKenzie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton_McKenzie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton_McKenzie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Minister of Sport, Arts and Culture,Gayton McKenziehasreacted to the announcementof South Africa's greatest ever Olympian,Tatjana Smith's,retirement from competitive swimming.\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 553, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 462, \"end\": 474, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.087871280697648e-13, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 491, \"end\": 499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999840442798, \"rank\": 1.5955856349660668e-08, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Enjoy the Paris Olympic Games 2024 experience at your favourite ATKV Resort!\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 631, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 619, \"end\": 623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ATKV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Retirement is always a deeply personal decision for any athlete, and no one could say that Smith has not achieved greatness.\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 757, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She steps off the podium as the greatest Olympian produced by South Africa with two gold medals and two silvers.\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 871, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 800, \"end\": 808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999840442798, \"rank\": 1.5955856349660668e-08, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 821, \"end\": 833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.087871280697648e-13, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Only a breath and a heartbeat stood between her and all four of her medals being gold,\\\" said McKenzie.\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 976, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are so proud of you, and I hope to meet you soon to shake your hand as your biggest fan.\\\"\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 1071, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Minister added that it would be wonderful if Smith would use her relatively young retirement as an opportunity to give back and encourage the next generation of young swimmers, especially girls, to whom she is justifiably a role model and idol.\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1321, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Enjoy your much-deserved retirement, Tatjana.\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1369, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This country shall never forget your excellence, and we need to tap into your experience and winning attitude,\\\" concluded Gayton McKenzie.\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1510, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1494, \"end\": 1509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton_McKenzie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gayton McKenzie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton_McKenzie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton_McKenzie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team South Africa left the Paris Olympics 2024 with one gold medal, three silvers and two bronzes.\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1610, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1512, \"end\": 1529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_baseball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Team South Africa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_baseball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_baseball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tatjana Smith\\u00a0was the 'big' winner for South Africa, collecting gold in the women's 100m breaststroke and silver in the women's 200m breaststroke.\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1758, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1651, \"end\": 1663, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.087871280697648e-13, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those medals were worth a total ofR600 000to Smith thanks to Sascoc's financial incentives promised ahead of the Games to the country's 138 selected athletes.\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1918, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"South Africa finished in a tie for44thplace in the final medal table alongsideJamaicaandThailand.\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 2017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1920, \"end\": 1932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.087871280697648e-13, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the latest Paris Olympics 2024 news, bookmarkThe South African website'sdedicated section for free-to-read content  WIN R2 000: Take The South African's SASSA Survey  The South African is hiring!\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2218, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2139, \"end\": 2142, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"score\": 0.9999999269552999, \"rank\": 5.444991545325608e-08, \"text\": \"WIN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\"}, {\"begin\": 2143, \"end\": 2145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\", \"score\": 0.9995325971695496, \"rank\": 0.00043297843966926854, \"text\": \"R2\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Freelance writing positions available  Follow The South African on Facebook for the latest loc